  "secondName": "Venomous Rose",
  "description": "Clarice found her way to the mansion of a lord. For a long, long time, the lord kept her as his servant, but she was so clumsy he sold her away, to a noble couple who needed a handmaiden for their daughter Ludmilla.\n\nEven though she was a terrible maid, Ludmilla showed Clarice great kindness. She let her borrow her books and do her hair, and over time, they became the best of friends.\n\nUntil she grew up and didn't want her anymore. Until she tried to run away.\n\nWhy would she do that? Weren't they friends? Was she a bad girl again?\n\nWhy... why... why why why whywhywhywhywh—",
